<li id="cite_note-SASLguestimate-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-SASLguestimate_14-0">^</a></b> <span class="citation" id="CITEREFOlivier2007">Olivier, Jaco (2007), <a href="http://www.cyberserv.co.za/users/~jako/lang/signlanguage/index.htm" class="external text" rel="nofollow"><i>South African Sign Language</i></a><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://www.cyberserv.co.za/users/~jako/lang/signlanguage/index.htm" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.cyberserv.co.za/users/~jako/lang/signlanguage/index.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved 2007-10-09</span></span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=South+African+Sign+Language&amp;rft.aulast=Olivier&amp;rft.aufirst=Jaco&amp;rft.au=Olivier%2C%26%2332%3BJaco&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cyberserv.co.za%2Fusers%2F%7Ejako%2Flang%2Fsignlanguage%2Findex.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:South_African_Sign_Language"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15">^</a></b> (1987). A Loss for Words: The Story of Deafness in a Family. New York: HarperPerennial. p. 31. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0060914254" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-06-091425-4</a>.</li>
</ol>
